043package org.parboiled.examples.java;
044
045import org.parboiled.Rule;
046import org.parboiled.annotations.BuildParseTree;
047import org.parboiled.annotations.DontLabel;
048import org.parboiled.annotations.MemoMismatches;
049import org.parboiled.annotations.SuppressNode;
050import org.parboiled.annotations.SuppressSubnodes;
051import org.parboiled.parser.BaseParser;
052
053@SuppressWarnings({"InfiniteRecursion"})
054@BuildParseTree
055public class JavaParser extends BaseParser<Object> {
056
057    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
058    //  Compilation Unit
059    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
060
061    public Rule CompilationUnit() {
062        return Sequence(
063                Spacing(),
064                Optional(PackageDeclaration()),
065                ZeroOrMore(ImportDeclaration()),
066                ZeroOrMore(TypeDeclaration()),
067                EOI
068        );
069    }
070
071    Rule PackageDeclaration() {
072        return Sequence(ZeroOrMore(Annotation()), Sequence(PACKAGE, QualifiedIdentifier(), SEMI));
073    }
074
075    Rule ImportDeclaration() {
076        return Sequence(
077                IMPORT,
078                Optional(STATIC),
079                QualifiedIdentifier(),
080                Optional(DOT, STAR),
081                SEMI
082        );
083    }
084
085    Rule TypeDeclaration() {
086        return FirstOf(
087                Sequence(
088                        ZeroOrMore(Modifier()),
089                        FirstOf(
090                                ClassDeclaration(),
091                                EnumDeclaration(),
092                                InterfaceDeclaration(),
093                                AnnotationTypeDeclaration()
094                        )
095                ),
096                SEMI
097        );
098    }
099
100    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
101    //  Class Declaration
102    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
103
104    Rule ClassDeclaration() {
105        return Sequence(
106                CLASS,
107                Identifier(),
108                Optional(TypeParameters()),
109                Optional(EXTENDS, ClassType()),
110                Optional(IMPLEMENTS, ClassTypeList()),
111                ClassBody()
112        );
113    }
114
115    Rule ClassBody() {
116        return Sequence(LWING, ZeroOrMore(ClassBodyDeclaration()), RWING);
117    }
118
119    Rule ClassBodyDeclaration() {
120        return FirstOf(
121                SEMI,
122                Sequence(Optional(STATIC), Block()),
123                Sequence(ZeroOrMore(Modifier()), MemberDecl())
124        );
125    }
126
127    Rule MemberDecl() {
128        return FirstOf(
129                Sequence(TypeParameters(), GenericMethodOrConstructorRest()),
130                Sequence(Type(), Identifier(), MethodDeclaratorRest()),
131                Sequence(Type(), VariableDeclarators(), SEMI),
132                Sequence(VOID, Identifier(), VoidMethodDeclaratorRest()),
133                Sequence(Identifier(), ConstructorDeclaratorRest()),
134                InterfaceDeclaration(),
135                ClassDeclaration(),
136                EnumDeclaration(),
137                AnnotationTypeDeclaration()
138        );
139    }
140
141    Rule GenericMethodOrConstructorRest() {
142        return FirstOf(
143                Sequence(FirstOf(Type(), VOID), Identifier(), MethodDeclaratorRest()),
144                Sequence(Identifier(), ConstructorDeclaratorRest())
145        );
146    }
147
148    Rule MethodDeclaratorRest() {
149        return Sequence(
150                FormalParameters(),
151                ZeroOrMore(Dim()),
152                Optional(THROWS, ClassTypeList()),
153                FirstOf(MethodBody(), SEMI)
154        );
155    }
156
157    Rule VoidMethodDeclaratorRest() {
158        return Sequence(
159                FormalParameters(),
160                Optional(THROWS, ClassTypeList()),
161                FirstOf(MethodBody(), SEMI)
162        );
163    }
164
165    Rule ConstructorDeclaratorRest() {
166        return Sequence(FormalParameters(), Optional(THROWS, ClassTypeList()), MethodBody());
167    }
168
169    Rule MethodBody() {
170        return Block();
171    }
172
173    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
174    //  Interface Declaration
175    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
176
177    Rule InterfaceDeclaration() {
178        return Sequence(
179                INTERFACE,
180                Identifier(),
181                Optional(TypeParameters()),
182                Optional(EXTENDS, ClassTypeList()),
183                InterfaceBody()
184        );
185    }
186
187    Rule InterfaceBody() {
188        return Sequence(LWING, ZeroOrMore(InterfaceBodyDeclaration()), RWING);
189    }
190
191    Rule InterfaceBodyDeclaration() {
192        return FirstOf(
193                Sequence(ZeroOrMore(Modifier()), InterfaceMemberDecl()),
194                SEMI
195        );
196    }
197
198    Rule InterfaceMemberDecl() {
199        return FirstOf(
200                InterfaceMethodOrFieldDecl(),
201                InterfaceGenericMethodDecl(),
202                Sequence(VOID, Identifier(), VoidInterfaceMethodDeclaratorsRest()),
203                InterfaceDeclaration(),
204                AnnotationTypeDeclaration(),
205                ClassDeclaration(),
206                EnumDeclaration()
207        );
208    }
209
210    Rule InterfaceMethodOrFieldDecl() {
211        return Sequence(Sequence(Type(), Identifier()), InterfaceMethodOrFieldRest());
212    }
213
214    Rule InterfaceMethodOrFieldRest() {
215        return FirstOf(
216                Sequence(ConstantDeclaratorsRest(), SEMI),
217                InterfaceMethodDeclaratorRest()
218        );
219    }
220
221    Rule InterfaceMethodDeclaratorRest() {
222        return Sequence(
223                FormalParameters(),
224                ZeroOrMore(Dim()),
225                Optional(THROWS, ClassTypeList()),
226                SEMI
227        );
228    }
229
230    Rule InterfaceGenericMethodDecl() {
231        return Sequence(TypeParameters(), FirstOf(Type(), VOID), Identifier(), InterfaceMethodDeclaratorRest());
232    }
233
234    Rule VoidInterfaceMethodDeclaratorsRest() {
235        return Sequence(FormalParameters(), Optional(THROWS, ClassTypeList()), SEMI);
236    }
237
238    Rule ConstantDeclaratorsRest() {
239        return Sequence(ConstantDeclaratorRest(), ZeroOrMore(COMMA, ConstantDeclarator()));
240    }
241
242    Rule ConstantDeclarator() {
243        return Sequence(Identifier(), ConstantDeclaratorRest());
244    }
245
246    Rule ConstantDeclaratorRest() {
247        return Sequence(ZeroOrMore(Dim()), EQU, VariableInitializer());
248    }
249
250    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
251    //  Enum Declaration
252    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
253
254    Rule EnumDeclaration() {
255        return Sequence(
256                ENUM,
257                Identifier(),
258                Optional(IMPLEMENTS, ClassTypeList()),
259                EnumBody()
260        );
261    }
262
263    Rule EnumBody() {
264        return Sequence(
265                LWING,
266                Optional(EnumConstants()),
267                Optional(COMMA),
268                Optional(EnumBodyDeclarations()),
269                RWING
270        );
271    }
272
273    Rule EnumConstants() {
274        return Sequence(EnumConstant(), ZeroOrMore(COMMA, EnumConstant()));
275    }
276
277    Rule EnumConstant() {
278        return Sequence(
279                ZeroOrMore(Annotation()),
280                Identifier(),
281                Optional(Arguments()),
282                Optional(ClassBody())
283        );
284    }
285
286    Rule EnumBodyDeclarations() {
287        return Sequence(SEMI, ZeroOrMore(ClassBodyDeclaration()));
288    }
289
290    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
291    //  Variable Declarations
292    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------    
293
294    Rule LocalVariableDeclarationStatement() {
295        return Sequence(ZeroOrMore(FirstOf(FINAL, Annotation())), Type(), VariableDeclarators(), SEMI);
296    }
297
298    Rule VariableDeclarators() {
299        return Sequence(VariableDeclarator(), ZeroOrMore(COMMA, VariableDeclarator()));
300    }
301
302    Rule VariableDeclarator() {
303        return Sequence(Identifier(), ZeroOrMore(Dim()), Optional(EQU, VariableInitializer()));
304    }
305
306    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
307    //  Formal Parameters
308    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
309
310    Rule FormalParameters() {
311        return Sequence(LPAR, Optional(FormalParameterDecls()), RPAR);
312    }
313
314    Rule FormalParameter() {
315        return Sequence(ZeroOrMore(FirstOf(FINAL, Annotation())), Type(), VariableDeclaratorId());
316    }
317
318    Rule FormalParameterDecls() {
319        return Sequence(ZeroOrMore(FirstOf(FINAL, Annotation())), Type(), FormalParameterDeclsRest());
320    }
321
322    Rule FormalParameterDeclsRest() {
323        return FirstOf(
324                Sequence(VariableDeclaratorId(), Optional(COMMA, FormalParameterDecls())),
325                Sequence(ELLIPSIS, VariableDeclaratorId())
326        );
327    }
328
329    Rule VariableDeclaratorId() {
330        return Sequence(Identifier(), ZeroOrMore(Dim()));
331    }
332
333    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
334    //  Statements
335    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------    
336
337    Rule Block() {
338        return Sequence(LWING, BlockStatements(), RWING);
339    }
340
341    Rule BlockStatements() {
342        return ZeroOrMore(BlockStatement());
343    }
344
345    Rule BlockStatement() {
346        return FirstOf(
347                LocalVariableDeclarationStatement(),
348                Sequence(ZeroOrMore(Modifier()), FirstOf(ClassDeclaration(), EnumDeclaration())),
349                Statement()
350        );
351    }
352
353    Rule Statement() {
354        return FirstOf(
355                Block(),
356                Sequence(ASSERT, Expression(), Optional(COLON, Expression()), SEMI),
357                Sequence(IF, ParExpression(), Statement(), Optional(ELSE, Statement())),
358                Sequence(FOR, LPAR, Optional(ForInit()), SEMI, Optional(Expression()), SEMI, Optional(ForUpdate()),
359                        RPAR, Statement()),
360                Sequence(FOR, LPAR, FormalParameter(), COLON, Expression(), RPAR, Statement()),
361                Sequence(WHILE, ParExpression(), Statement()),
362                Sequence(DO, Statement(), WHILE, ParExpression(), SEMI),
363                Sequence(TRY, Block(),
364                        FirstOf(Sequence(OneOrMore(Catch_()), Optional(Finally_())), Finally_())),
365                Sequence(SWITCH, ParExpression(), LWING, SwitchBlockStatementGroups(), RWING),
366                Sequence(SYNCHRONIZED, ParExpression(), Block()),
367                Sequence(RETURN, Optional(Expression()), SEMI),
368                Sequence(THROW, Expression(), SEMI),
369                Sequence(BREAK, Optional(Identifier()), SEMI),
370                Sequence(CONTINUE, Optional(Identifier()), SEMI),
371                Sequence(Sequence(Identifier(), COLON), Statement()),
372                Sequence(StatementExpression(), SEMI),
373                SEMI
374        );
375    }
376
377    Rule Catch_() {
378        return Sequence(CATCH, LPAR, FormalParameter(), RPAR, Block());
379    }
380
381    Rule Finally_() {
382        return Sequence(FINALLY, Block());
383    }
384
385    Rule SwitchBlockStatementGroups() {
386        return ZeroOrMore(SwitchBlockStatementGroup());
387    }
388
389    Rule SwitchBlockStatementGroup() {
390        return Sequence(SwitchLabel(), BlockStatements());
391    }
392
393    Rule SwitchLabel() {
394        return FirstOf(
395                Sequence(CASE, ConstantExpression(), COLON),
396                Sequence(CASE, EnumConstantName(), COLON),
397                Sequence(DEFAULT, COLON)
398        );
399    }
400
401    Rule ForInit() {
402        return FirstOf(
403                Sequence(ZeroOrMore(FirstOf(FINAL, Annotation())), Type(), VariableDeclarators()),
404                Sequence(StatementExpression(), ZeroOrMore(COMMA, StatementExpression()))
405        );
406    }
407
408    Rule ForUpdate() {
409        return Sequence(StatementExpression(), ZeroOrMore(COMMA, StatementExpression()));
410    }
411
412    Rule EnumConstantName() {
413        return Identifier();
414    }
415
416    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
417    //  Expressions
418    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
419
420    // The following is more generous than the definition in section 14.8,
421    // which allows only specific forms of Expression.
422
423    Rule StatementExpression() {
424        return Expression();
425    }
426
427    Rule ConstantExpression() {
428        return Expression();
429    }
430
431    // The following definition is part of the modification in JLS Chapter 18
432    // to minimize look ahead. In JLS Chapter 15.27, Expression is defined
433    // as AssignmentExpression, which is effectively defined as
434    // (LeftHandSide AssignmentOperator)* ConditionalExpression.
435    // The following is obtained by allowing ANY ConditionalExpression
436    // as LeftHandSide, which results in accepting statements like 5 = a.
437
438    Rule Expression() {
439        return Sequence(
440                ConditionalExpression(),
441                ZeroOrMore(AssignmentOperator(), ConditionalExpression())
442        );
443    }
444
445    Rule AssignmentOperator() {
446        return FirstOf(EQU, PLUSEQU, MINUSEQU, STAREQU, DIVEQU, ANDEQU, OREQU, HATEQU, MODEQU, SLEQU, SREQU, BSREQU);
447    }
448
449    Rule ConditionalExpression() {
450        return Sequence(
451                ConditionalOrExpression(),
452                ZeroOrMore(QUERY, Expression(), COLON, ConditionalOrExpression())
453        );
454    }
455
456    Rule ConditionalOrExpression() {
457        return Sequence(
458                ConditionalAndExpression(),
459                ZeroOrMore(OROR, ConditionalAndExpression())
460        );
461    }
462
463    Rule ConditionalAndExpression() {
464        return Sequence(
465                InclusiveOrExpression(),
466                ZeroOrMore(ANDAND, InclusiveOrExpression())
467        );
468    }
469
470    Rule InclusiveOrExpression() {
471        return Sequence(
472                ExclusiveOrExpression(),
473                ZeroOrMore(OR, ExclusiveOrExpression())
474        );
475    }
476
477    Rule ExclusiveOrExpression() {
478        return Sequence(
479                AndExpression(),
480                ZeroOrMore(HAT, AndExpression())
481        );
482    }
483
484    Rule AndExpression() {
485        return Sequence(
486                EqualityExpression(),
487                ZeroOrMore(AND, EqualityExpression())
488        );
489    }
490
491    Rule EqualityExpression() {
492        return Sequence(
493                RelationalExpression(),
494                ZeroOrMore(FirstOf(EQUAL, NOTEQUAL), RelationalExpression())
495        );
496    }
497
498    Rule RelationalExpression() {
499        return Sequence(
500                ShiftExpression(),
501                ZeroOrMore(
502                        FirstOf(
503                                Sequence(FirstOf(LE, GE, LT, GT), ShiftExpression()),
504                                Sequence(INSTANCEOF, ReferenceType())
505                        )
506                )
507        );
508    }
509
510    Rule ShiftExpression() {
511        return Sequence(
512                AdditiveExpression(),
513                ZeroOrMore(FirstOf(SL, SR, BSR), AdditiveExpression())
514        );
515    }
516
517    Rule AdditiveExpression() {
518        return Sequence(
519                MultiplicativeExpression(),
520                ZeroOrMore(FirstOf(PLUS, MINUS), MultiplicativeExpression())
521        );
522    }
523
524    Rule MultiplicativeExpression() {
525        return Sequence(
526                UnaryExpression(),
527                ZeroOrMore(FirstOf(STAR, DIV, MOD), UnaryExpression())
528        );
529    }
530
531    Rule UnaryExpression() {
532        return FirstOf(
533                Sequence(PrefixOp(), UnaryExpression()),
534                Sequence(LPAR, Type(), RPAR, UnaryExpression()),
535                Sequence(Primary(), ZeroOrMore(Selector()), ZeroOrMore(PostFixOp()))
536        );
537    }
538
539    Rule Primary() {
540        return FirstOf(
541                ParExpression(),
542                Sequence(
543                        NonWildcardTypeArguments(),
544                        FirstOf(ExplicitGenericInvocationSuffix(), Sequence(THIS, Arguments()))
545                ),
546                Sequence(THIS, Optional(Arguments())),
547                Sequence(SUPER, SuperSuffix()),
548                Literal(),
549                Sequence(NEW, Creator()),
550                Sequence(QualifiedIdentifier(), Optional(IdentifierSuffix())),
551                Sequence(BasicType(), ZeroOrMore(Dim()), DOT, CLASS),
552                Sequence(VOID, DOT, CLASS)
553        );
554    }
555
556    Rule IdentifierSuffix() {
557        return FirstOf(
558                Sequence(LBRK,
559                        FirstOf(
560                                Sequence(RBRK, ZeroOrMore(Dim()), DOT, CLASS),
561                                Sequence(Expression(), RBRK)
562                        )
563                ),
564                Arguments(),
565                Sequence(
566                        DOT,
567                        FirstOf(
568                                CLASS,
569                                ExplicitGenericInvocation(),
570                                THIS,
571                                Sequence(SUPER, Arguments()),
572                                Sequence(NEW, Optional(NonWildcardTypeArguments()), InnerCreator())
573                        )
574                )
575        );
576    }
577
578    Rule ExplicitGenericInvocation() {
579        return Sequence(NonWildcardTypeArguments(), ExplicitGenericInvocationSuffix());
580    }
581
582    Rule NonWildcardTypeArguments() {
583        return Sequence(LPOINT, ReferenceType(), ZeroOrMore(COMMA, ReferenceType()), RPOINT);
584    }
585
586    Rule ExplicitGenericInvocationSuffix() {
587        return FirstOf(
588                Sequence(SUPER, SuperSuffix()),
589                Sequence(Identifier(), Arguments())
590        );
591    }
592
593    Rule PrefixOp() {
594        return FirstOf(INC, DEC, BANG, TILDA, PLUS, MINUS);
595    }
596
597    Rule PostFixOp() {
598        return FirstOf(INC, DEC);
599    }
600
601    Rule Selector() {
602        return FirstOf(
603                Sequence(DOT, Identifier(), Optional(Arguments())),
604                Sequence(DOT, ExplicitGenericInvocation()),
605                Sequence(DOT, THIS),
606                Sequence(DOT, SUPER, SuperSuffix()),
607                Sequence(DOT, NEW, Optional(NonWildcardTypeArguments()), InnerCreator()),
608                DimExpr()
609        );
610    }
611
612    Rule SuperSuffix() {
613        return FirstOf(Arguments(), Sequence(DOT, Identifier(), Optional(Arguments())));
614    }
615
616    @MemoMismatches
617    Rule BasicType() {
618        return Sequence(
619                FirstOf("byte", "short", "char", "int", "long", "float", "double", "boolean"),
620                TestNot(LetterOrDigit()),
621                Spacing()
622        );
623    }
624
625    Rule Arguments() {
626        return Sequence(
627                LPAR,
628                Optional(Expression(), ZeroOrMore(COMMA, Expression())),
629                RPAR
630        );
631    }
632
633    Rule Creator() {
634        return FirstOf(
635                Sequence(Optional(NonWildcardTypeArguments()), CreatedName(), ClassCreatorRest()),
636                Sequence(Optional(NonWildcardTypeArguments()), FirstOf(ClassType(), BasicType()), ArrayCreatorRest())
637        );
638    }
639
640    Rule CreatedName() {
641        return Sequence(
642                Identifier(), Optional(NonWildcardTypeArguments()),
643                ZeroOrMore(DOT, Identifier(), Optional(NonWildcardTypeArguments()))
644        );
645    }
646
647    Rule InnerCreator() {
648        return Sequence(Identifier(), ClassCreatorRest());
649    }
650
651    // The following is more generous than JLS 15.10. According to that definition,
652    // BasicType must be followed by at least one DimExpr or by ArrayInitializer.
653    Rule ArrayCreatorRest() {
654        return Sequence(
655                LBRK,
656                FirstOf(
657                        Sequence(RBRK, ZeroOrMore(Dim()), ArrayInitializer()),
658                        Sequence(Expression(), RBRK, ZeroOrMore(DimExpr()), ZeroOrMore(Dim()))
659                )
660        );
661    }
662
663    Rule ClassCreatorRest() {
664        return Sequence(Arguments(), Optional(ClassBody()));
665    }
666
667    Rule ArrayInitializer() {
668        return Sequence(
669                LWING,
670                Optional(
671                    VariableInitializer(),
672                    ZeroOrMore(COMMA, VariableInitializer())
673                ),
674                Optional(COMMA),
675                RWING
676        );
677    }
678
679    Rule VariableInitializer() {
680        return FirstOf(ArrayInitializer(), Expression());
681    }
682
683    Rule ParExpression() {
684        return Sequence(LPAR, Expression(), RPAR);
685    }
686
687    Rule QualifiedIdentifier() {
688        return Sequence(Identifier(), ZeroOrMore(DOT, Identifier()));
689    }
690
691    Rule Dim() {
692        return Sequence(LBRK, RBRK);
693    }
694
695    Rule DimExpr() {
696        return Sequence(LBRK, Expression(), RBRK);
697    }
698
699    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
700    //  Types and Modifiers
701    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
702
703    Rule Type() {
704        return Sequence(FirstOf(BasicType(), ClassType()), ZeroOrMore(Dim()));
705    }
706
707    Rule ReferenceType() {
708        return FirstOf(
709                Sequence(BasicType(), OneOrMore(Dim())),
710                Sequence(ClassType(), ZeroOrMore(Dim()))
711        );
712    }
713
714    Rule ClassType() {
715        return Sequence(
716                Identifier(), Optional(TypeArguments()),
717                ZeroOrMore(DOT, Identifier(), Optional(TypeArguments()))
718        );
719    }
720
721    Rule ClassTypeList() {
722        return Sequence(ClassType(), ZeroOrMore(COMMA, ClassType()));
723    }
724
725    Rule TypeArguments() {
726        return Sequence(LPOINT, TypeArgument(), ZeroOrMore(COMMA, TypeArgument()), RPOINT);
727    }
728
729    Rule TypeArgument() {
730        return FirstOf(
731                ReferenceType(),
732                Sequence(QUERY, Optional(FirstOf(EXTENDS, SUPER), ReferenceType()))
733        );
734    }
735
736    Rule TypeParameters() {
737        return Sequence(LPOINT, TypeParameter(), ZeroOrMore(COMMA, TypeParameter()), RPOINT);
738    }
739
740    Rule TypeParameter() {
741        return Sequence(Identifier(), Optional(EXTENDS, Bound()));
742    }
743
744    Rule Bound() {
745        return Sequence(ClassType(), ZeroOrMore(AND, ClassType()));
746    }
747
748    // the following common definition of Modifier is part of the modification
749    // in JLS Chapter 18 to minimize look ahead. The main body of JLS has
750    // different lists of modifiers for different language elements.
751    Rule Modifier() {
752        return FirstOf(
753                Annotation(),
754                Sequence(
755                        FirstOf("public", "protected", "private", "static", "abstract", "final", "native",
756                                "synchronized", "transient", "volatile", "strictfp"),
757                        TestNot(LetterOrDigit()),
758                        Spacing()
759                )
760        );
761    }
762
763    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
764    //  Annotations
765    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------    
766
767    Rule AnnotationTypeDeclaration() {
768        return Sequence(AT, INTERFACE, Identifier(), AnnotationTypeBody());
769    }
770
771    Rule AnnotationTypeBody() {
772        return Sequence(LWING, ZeroOrMore(AnnotationTypeElementDeclaration()), RWING);
773    }
774
775    Rule AnnotationTypeElementDeclaration() {
776        return FirstOf(
777                Sequence(ZeroOrMore(Modifier()), AnnotationTypeElementRest()),
778                SEMI
779        );
780    }
781
782    Rule AnnotationTypeElementRest() {
783        return FirstOf(
784                Sequence(Type(), AnnotationMethodOrConstantRest(), SEMI),
785                ClassDeclaration(),
786                EnumDeclaration(),
787                InterfaceDeclaration(),
788                AnnotationTypeDeclaration()
789        );
790    }
791
792    Rule AnnotationMethodOrConstantRest() {
793        return FirstOf(AnnotationMethodRest(), AnnotationConstantRest());
794    }
795
796    Rule AnnotationMethodRest() {
797        return Sequence(Identifier(), LPAR, RPAR, Optional(DefaultValue()));
798    }
799
800    Rule AnnotationConstantRest() {
801        return VariableDeclarators();
802    }
803
804    Rule DefaultValue() {
805        return Sequence(DEFAULT, ElementValue());
806    }
807
808    @MemoMismatches
809    Rule Annotation() {
810        return Sequence(AT, QualifiedIdentifier(), Optional(AnnotationRest()));
811    }
812
813    Rule AnnotationRest() {
814        return FirstOf(NormalAnnotationRest(), SingleElementAnnotationRest());
815    }
816
817    Rule NormalAnnotationRest() {
818        return Sequence(LPAR, Optional(ElementValuePairs()), RPAR);
819    }
820
821    Rule ElementValuePairs() {
822        return Sequence(ElementValuePair(), ZeroOrMore(COMMA, ElementValuePair()));
823    }
824
825    Rule ElementValuePair() {
826        return Sequence(Identifier(), EQU, ElementValue());
827    }
828
829    Rule ElementValue() {
830        return FirstOf(ConditionalExpression(), Annotation(), ElementValueArrayInitializer());
831    }
832
833    Rule ElementValueArrayInitializer() {
834        return Sequence(LWING, Optional(ElementValues()), Optional(COMMA), RWING);
835    }
836
837    Rule ElementValues() {
838        return Sequence(ElementValue(), ZeroOrMore(COMMA, ElementValue()));
839    }
840
841    Rule SingleElementAnnotationRest() {
842        return Sequence(LPAR, ElementValue(), RPAR);
843    }
844
845    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
846    //  JLS 3.6-7  Spacing
847    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
848
849    @SuppressNode
850    Rule Spacing() {
851        return ZeroOrMore(FirstOf(
852
853                // whitespace
854                OneOrMore(AnyOf(" \t\r\n\f").label("Whitespace")),
855
856                // traditional comment
857                Sequence("/*", ZeroOrMore(TestNot("*/"), ANY), "*/"),
858
859                // end of line comment
860                Sequence(
861                        "//",
862                        ZeroOrMore(TestNot(AnyOf("\r\n")), ANY),
863                        FirstOf("\r\n", '\r', '\n', EOI)
864                )
865        ));
866    }

868    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
869    //  JLS 3.8  Identifiers
870    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
871
872    @SuppressSubnodes
873    @MemoMismatches
874    Rule Identifier() {
875        return Sequence(TestNot(Keyword()), Letter(), ZeroOrMore(LetterOrDigit()), Spacing());
876    }
877
878    // JLS defines letters and digits as Unicode characters recognized
879    // as such by special Java procedures.
880
881    Rule Letter() {
882        // switch to this "reduced" character space version for a ~10% parser performance speedup
883        //return FirstOf(CharRange('a', 'z'), CharRange('A', 'Z'), '_', '$');
884        return FirstOf(Sequence('\\', UnicodeEscape()), new JavaLetterMatcher());
885    }
886
887    @MemoMismatches
888    Rule LetterOrDigit() {
889        // switch to this "reduced" character space version for a ~10% parser performance speedup
890        //return FirstOf(CharRange('a', 'z'), CharRange('A', 'Z'), CharRange('0', '9'), '_', '$');
891        return FirstOf(Sequence('\\', UnicodeEscape()), new JavaLetterOrDigitMatcher());
892    }
893
894    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
895    //  JLS 3.9  Keywords
896    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
897
898    @MemoMismatches
899    Rule Keyword() {
900        return Sequence(
901                FirstOf("assert", "break", "case", "catch", "class", "const", "continue", "default", "do", "else",
902                        "enum", "extends", "finally", "final", "for", "goto", "if", "implements", "import", "interface",
903                        "instanceof", "new", "package", "return", "static", "super", "switch", "synchronized", "this",
904                        "throws", "throw", "try", "void", "while"),
905                TestNot(LetterOrDigit())
906        );
907    }
908
909    public final Rule ASSERT = Keyword("assert");
910    public final Rule BREAK = Keyword("break");
911    public final Rule CASE = Keyword("case");
912    public final Rule CATCH = Keyword("catch");
913    public final Rule CLASS = Keyword("class");
914    public final Rule CONTINUE = Keyword("continue");
915    public final Rule DEFAULT = Keyword("default");
916    public final Rule DO = Keyword("do");
917    public final Rule ELSE = Keyword("else");
918    public final Rule ENUM = Keyword("enum");
919    public final Rule EXTENDS = Keyword("extends");
920    public final Rule FINALLY = Keyword("finally");
921    public final Rule FINAL = Keyword("final");
922    public final Rule FOR = Keyword("for");
923    public final Rule IF = Keyword("if");
924    public final Rule IMPLEMENTS = Keyword("implements");
925    public final Rule IMPORT = Keyword("import");
926    public final Rule INTERFACE = Keyword("interface");
927    public final Rule INSTANCEOF = Keyword("instanceof");
928    public final Rule NEW = Keyword("new");
929    public final Rule PACKAGE = Keyword("package");
930    public final Rule RETURN = Keyword("return");
931    public final Rule STATIC = Keyword("static");
932    public final Rule SUPER = Keyword("super");
933    public final Rule SWITCH = Keyword("switch");
934    public final Rule SYNCHRONIZED = Keyword("synchronized");
935    public final Rule THIS = Keyword("this");
936    public final Rule THROWS = Keyword("throws");
937    public final Rule THROW = Keyword("throw");
938    public final Rule TRY = Keyword("try");
939    public final Rule VOID = Keyword("void");
940    public final Rule WHILE = Keyword("while");
941
942    @SuppressNode
943    @DontLabel
944    Rule Keyword(String keyword) {
945        return Terminal(keyword, LetterOrDigit());
946    }

948    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
949    //  JLS 3.10  Literals
950    //-------------------------------------------------------------------------
951
952    Rule Literal() {
953        return Sequence(
954                FirstOf(
955                        FloatLiteral(),
956                        IntegerLiteral(),
957                        CharLiteral(),
958                        StringLiteral(),
959                        Sequence("true", TestNot(LetterOrDigit())),
960                        Sequence("false", TestNot(LetterOrDigit())),
961                        Sequence("null", TestNot(LetterOrDigit()))
962                ),
963                Spacing()
964        );
965    }
966
967    @SuppressSubnodes
968    Rule IntegerLiteral() {
969        return Sequence(FirstOf(HexNumeral(), OctalNumeral(), DecimalNumeral()), Optional(AnyOf("lL")));
970    }
971
972    @SuppressSubnodes
973    Rule DecimalNumeral() {
974        return FirstOf('0', Sequence(CharRange('1', '9'), ZeroOrMore(Digit())));
975    }
976
977    @SuppressSubnodes
978
979    @MemoMismatches
980    Rule HexNumeral() {
981        return Sequence('0', IgnoreCase('x'), OneOrMore(HexDigit()));
982    }
983
984    Rule HexDigit() {
985        return FirstOf(CharRange('a', 'f'), CharRange('A', 'F'), CharRange('0', '9'));
986    }
987
988    @SuppressSubnodes
989    Rule OctalNumeral() {
990        return Sequence('0', OneOrMore(CharRange('0', '7')));
991    }
992
993    Rule FloatLiteral() {
994        return FirstOf(HexFloat(), DecimalFloat());
995    }
996
997    @SuppressSubnodes
998    Rule DecimalFloat() {
999        return FirstOf(
1000                Sequence(OneOrMore(Digit()), '.', ZeroOrMore(Digit()), Optional(Exponent()), Optional(AnyOf("fFdD"))),
1001                Sequence('.', OneOrMore(Digit()), Optional(Exponent()), Optional(AnyOf("fFdD"))),
1002                Sequence(OneOrMore(Digit()), Exponent(), Optional(AnyOf("fFdD"))),
1003                Sequence(OneOrMore(Digit()), Optional(Exponent()), AnyOf("fFdD"))
1004        );
1005    }
1006
1007    Rule Exponent() {
1008        return Sequence(AnyOf("eE"), Optional(AnyOf("+-")), OneOrMore(Digit()));
1009    }
1010
1011    Rule Digit() {
1012        return CharRange('0', '9');
1013    }
1014
1015    @SuppressSubnodes
1016    Rule HexFloat() {
1017        return Sequence(HexSignificant(), BinaryExponent(), Optional(AnyOf("fFdD")));
1018    }
1019
1020    Rule HexSignificant() {
1021        return FirstOf(
1022                Sequence(FirstOf("0x", "0X"), ZeroOrMore(HexDigit()), '.', OneOrMore(HexDigit())),
1023                Sequence(HexNumeral(), Optional('.'))
1024        );
1025    }
1026
1027    Rule BinaryExponent() {
1028        return Sequence(AnyOf("pP"), Optional(AnyOf("+-")), OneOrMore(Digit()));
1029    }
1030
1031    Rule CharLiteral() {
1032        return Sequence(
1033                '\'',
1034                FirstOf(Escape(), Sequence(TestNot(AnyOf("'\\")), ANY)).suppressSubnodes(),
1035                '\''
1036        );
1037    }
1038
1039    Rule StringLiteral() {
1040        return Sequence(
1041                '"',
1042                ZeroOrMore(
1043                        FirstOf(
1044                                Escape(),
1045                                Sequence(TestNot(AnyOf("\r\n\"\\")), ANY)
1046                        )
1047                ).suppressSubnodes(),
1048                '"'
1049        );
1050    }
1051
1052    Rule Escape() {
1053        return Sequence('\\', FirstOf(AnyOf("btnfr\"\'\\"), OctalEscape(), UnicodeEscape()));
1054    }
1055
1056    Rule OctalEscape() {
1057        return FirstOf(
1058                Sequence(CharRange('0', '3'), CharRange('0', '7'), CharRange('0', '7')),
1059                Sequence(CharRange('0', '7'), CharRange('0', '7')),
1060                CharRange('0', '7')
1061        );
1062    }
1063
1064    Rule UnicodeEscape() {
1065        return Sequence(OneOrMore('u'), HexDigit(), HexDigit(), HexDigit(), HexDigit());
1066    }

1072    final Rule AT = Terminal("@");
1073    final Rule AND = Terminal("&", AnyOf("=&"));
1074    final Rule ANDAND = Terminal("&&");
1075    final Rule ANDEQU = Terminal("&=");
1076    final Rule BANG = Terminal("!", Ch('='));
1077    final Rule BSR = Terminal(">>>", Ch('='));
1078    final Rule BSREQU = Terminal(">>>=");
1079    final Rule COLON = Terminal(":");
1080    final Rule COMMA = Terminal(",");
1081    final Rule DEC = Terminal("--");
1082    final Rule DIV = Terminal("/", Ch('='));
1083    final Rule DIVEQU = Terminal("/=");
1084    final Rule DOT = Terminal(".");
1085    final Rule ELLIPSIS = Terminal("...");
1086    final Rule EQU = Terminal("=", Ch('='));
1087    final Rule EQUAL = Terminal("==");
1088    final Rule GE = Terminal(">=");
1089    final Rule GT = Terminal(">", AnyOf("=>"));
1090    final Rule HAT = Terminal("^", Ch('='));
1091    final Rule HATEQU = Terminal("^=");
1092    final Rule INC = Terminal("++");
1093    final Rule LBRK = Terminal("[");
1094    final Rule LE = Terminal("<=");
1095    final Rule LPAR = Terminal("(");
1096    final Rule LPOINT = Terminal("<");
1097    final Rule LT = Terminal("<", AnyOf("=<"));
1098    final Rule LWING = Terminal("{");
1099    final Rule MINUS = Terminal("-", AnyOf("=-"));
1100    final Rule MINUSEQU = Terminal("-=");
1101    final Rule MOD = Terminal("%", Ch('='));
1102    final Rule MODEQU = Terminal("%=");
1103    final Rule NOTEQUAL = Terminal("!=");
1104    final Rule OR = Terminal("|", AnyOf("=|"));
1105    final Rule OREQU = Terminal("|=");
1106    final Rule OROR = Terminal("||");
1107    final Rule PLUS = Terminal("+", AnyOf("=+"));
1108    final Rule PLUSEQU = Terminal("+=");
1109    final Rule QUERY = Terminal("?");
1110    final Rule RBRK = Terminal("]");
1111    final Rule RPAR = Terminal(")");
1112    final Rule RPOINT = Terminal(">");
1113    final Rule RWING = Terminal("}");
1114    final Rule SEMI = Terminal(";");
1115    final Rule SL = Terminal("<<", Ch('='));
1116    final Rule SLEQU = Terminal("<<=");
1117    final Rule SR = Terminal(">>", AnyOf("=>"));
1118    final Rule SREQU = Terminal(">>=");
1119    final Rule STAR = Terminal("*", Ch('='));
1120    final Rule STAREQU = Terminal("*=");
1121    final Rule TILDA = Terminal("~");

1126
1127    @Override
1128    protected Rule fromCharLiteral(char c) {
1129        // turn of creation of parse tree nodes for single characters
1130        return super.fromCharLiteral(c).suppressNode();
1131    }

1133    @SuppressNode
1134    @DontLabel
1135    Rule Terminal(String string) {
1136        return Sequence(string, Spacing()).label('\'' + string + '\'');
1137    }
1138
1139    @SuppressNode
1140    @DontLabel
1141    Rule Terminal(String string, Rule mustNotFollow) {
1142        return Sequence(string, TestNot(mustNotFollow), Spacing()).label('\'' + string + '\'');
1143    }
